          "@type": "Question", 
          "name": "Is GoVal AI compliant with 21 CFR Part 11 regulations?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes, GoVal AI is designed to meet 21 CFR Part 11 requirements with built-in electronic signatures, audit trails, data integrity controls, and validation protocols specifically for AI systems in GxP environments."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What types of validation can GoVal AI automate?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "GoVal AI can automate computer system validation, equipment qualification, process validation, data integrity assessments, risk-based validation approaches, and regulatory documentation generation across pharmaceutical and life sciences operations."
